    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Doton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 17 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 5 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 17</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You firmly plant your feet into the ground, gaining a +12 bonus to checks made to resist bull rush, grapple, overrun and trip checks. If your feet leave the ground (you move or are bull rushed, tripped, etc), the technique immediately ends.</p>\n\n\n\n",
